---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Bookkeeping Services Toronto | Cloud Accounting | Hills Tax"
  description="Professional bookkeeping services in Toronto. Monthly reconciliation, cloud accounting setup, payroll processing, and financial reporting. Keep your business finances organized."
  keywords="bookkeeping services Toronto, cloud accounting Toronto, QuickBooks bookkeeper, small business bookkeeping"
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Bookkeeping Services</h1>
      <p>Accurate, reliable bookkeeping to keep your business finances organized and tax-ready year-round.</p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Get a Quote</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-block">
        <h2>Professional Bookkeeping for Growing Businesses</h2>
        <p>Good bookkeeping is the foundation of sound financial management. Our bookkeeping services ensure your financial records are accurate, up-to-date, and ready for tax season. We use modern cloud-based accounting software to give you real-time visibility into your business finances, so you can make informed decisions with confidence.</p>
        <p>Whether you're a freelancer, small business, or growing company, our bookkeeping team handles the numbers so you can focus on what you do best â€” running your business.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt-bg">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What's Included</h2>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Monthly Bookkeeping</h3>
          <p>Regular recording and categorization of all business transactions, ensuring your books are always current and accurate.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Bank Reconciliation</h3>
          <p>Monthly reconciliation of all bank accounts and credit cards to catch discrepancies and ensure accuracy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Financial Statements</h3>
          <p>Monthly or quarterly income statements, balance sheets, and cash flow reports so you always know where your business stands.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Cloud Accounting Setup</h3>
          <p>We set up and manage your QuickBooks Online, Xero, or other cloud accounting platform for seamless collaboration.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Accounts Payable & Receivable</h3>
          <p>Track what you owe and what's owed to you. We manage invoicing follow-ups and vendor payment tracking.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>HST/GST Tracking & Filing</h3>
          <p>Accurate tracking of sales tax collected and paid, with timely filing of HST/GST returns to the CRA.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Payroll Processing</h3>
          <p>Complete payroll services including calculations, remittances, T4 preparation, and Record of Employment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Year-End Package</h3>
          <p>Comprehensive year-end financial package prepared and ready for your tax accountant, ensuring a smooth tax filing process.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Why Outsource Your Bookkeeping?</h2>
      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Save Time</h3>
          <p>Free up hours every week to focus on growing your business instead of managing receipts and spreadsheets.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Reduce Errors</h3>
          <p>Professional bookkeepers catch mistakes that can lead to costly tax issues or poor business decisions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="9" y1="15" x2="15" y2="15"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Tax Ready</h3>
          <p>Your books are always organized and ready for tax season, reducing stress and accounting fees at year-end.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Better Decisions</h3>
          <p>Accurate, timely financial data gives you the insights you need to make smart business decisions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container cta-content">
      <h2>Get Your Books in Order</h2>
      <p>Contact us today for a free bookkeeping consultation and customized quote for your business.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:+1XXXXXXXXXX" class="btn btn-secondary">Call (XXX) XXX-XXXX</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: var(--olive);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 5rem 0 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .page-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--olive) 0%, var(--olive-dark) 100%);
  }
  .page-hero > .container { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .page-hero h1 { color: var(--white); font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-hero p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 1.15rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }

  .alt-bg { background: var(--white); }

  .intro-block { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .intro-block h2 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .intro-block p { color: var(--gray-600); font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

  .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .feature-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
  }
  .feature-card h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--olive); }
  .feature-card p { color: var(--gray-600); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .benefits-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .benefit { text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem; }
  .benefit-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--leaf-pale);
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: var(--olive);
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  }
  .benefit h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--olive); }
  .benefit p { color: var(--gray-600); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .cta-section {
    background: var(--olive);
    color: var(--white);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--olive) 0%, var(--olive-dark) 100%);
  }
  .cta-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .cta-content h2 { color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cta-content p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .benefits-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
</style>
